2. prnor.xml for describing the transformation between 
the NOR elements and the ontology elements. It has 
only one section
- PRNOR section, that includes the description 
of the transformations from the NOR schema 
components (e.g., schema entities, atributes and 
relations) into ontology elements (e.g., classes, 
object properties, datatype properties, and 
individuals). Additionally it indicates the 
transformation approach, e.g., TBox, ABox, or 
Population.
